{"id": "1513509747083448340", "channel_id": "1513509747083448340", "author_id": "206110356127350785", "author_name": "mekyu", "content": "大家好，\n\n我在浏览兑换商店时，由于粗心大意、鼠标双击故障，加上作为新玩家缺乏经验，我不小心用大约 5000 点“沉积物”（sediment）兑换了数千件“悖论”（Paradox）套装部件。这是一次误操作，我想知道是否可以进行数据回档，或者是否有相关渠道可以申请处理。我目前还没有使用或分解这些“悖论”套装部件。\n\n我平时在购买物品时非常谨慎，因为担心因经验不足而做出错误的投资决定，所以这次失误对我来说损失相当惨重……\n\n这段文字是使用翻译工具生成的，如有不准确之处，敬请见谅。\n\nHello everyone, \n\ni went through the exchange shop and in a mix of carelessness, a malfunction double click on mouse and general lack of knowledge as a new player i purchased thousands of \"Paradox\" Set pieces with around 5000 sediment. This was an accidental purchase and i was wondering if something like a rollback is possible or i can apply for it somewhere. I have not touched the paradox set pieces yet or dismantled them. \n\nI am very careful with what i purchase as my lack of knowledge makes me scared of making bad decisions in terms of investement, so this is quite the big hit for me...", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T11:47:23.356000+00:00", "thread_id": "1513509747083448340"}
